  ('Binh Rey', 'General Manager', 'Managing Director, Applied Marks ● Trade Mark Attorney with branding expertise ● Expertise in branding, former marketer turned Trade Mark Attorney ● Queen of Trade Marks® ● Speaker & Trainer ● Executive Board member · When you protect your brand, you protect your future success. That’s why trademarks and brand protections are not just for big, multi-national companies. Every business has the right to operate without the fear of infringement. With over 15 years of marketing industry experience, 12 years of trademark industry experience, and over 1,500 trademarks filed, I inform, empower, and protect businesses of all sizes as General Manager at Applied Marks. Applied Marks is a leading provider of online trade', 'Melbourne, Victoria, Australia', '15+ years operating experience in ANZ and international markets.', ARRAY['Active Advisor', 'Legal'], 'https://linkedin.com/in/binhrey', NULL, NULL, 'Applied Marks', FALSE, '[{"name": "Applied Marks"}, {"name": "Business Blueprint"}]'::jsonb, 'uk', ARRAY['uk', 'australia'], NULL, 'binh-rey', 'Active Advisor', ARRAY['international_entrant'], TRUE, FALSE),
