  ('Bertrand Raoult', 'Senior Regional Manager - Australia', 'Senior Regional Manager - Australia at Export Development Canada · A MBA qualified senior accounts and sales professional with 26 years international experience, I have a proven track record of delivering growth and profitability through building long-term relationships with clients, based on credibility, trust and openness.Comfortable working at all levels of organisations, I have developed strong negotiation, presentation and stakeholder management skills that have been key factors in delivering value to both my employers and clients. Commercially astute, wit', 'Clovelly, New South Wales, Australia', 'Senior operator with extensive ANZ market experience.', ARRAY['Trade & Government', 'Cross-border'], 'https://linkedin.com/in/bertrandraoult', NULL, NULL, 'Export Development Canada | Exportation et développement Canada', FALSE, '[{"name": "Export Development Canada | Exportation et d\u00e9veloppement Canada"}, {"name": "Trade Commissioner Service | Service des d\u00e9l\u00e9gu\u00e9s commerciaux"}]'::jsonb, NULL, ARRAY['australia'], NULL, 'bertrand-raoult', 'Trade & Government', ARRAY['international_entrant'], TRUE, FALSE),
