  ('Charlie Crozier', 'Director', 'Founder & CEO | Web3 Evangelist | · Charlie holds extensive experience across the impact, blockchain technology, and finance industries. He has a depth of startup experience that adds a pedigree of understanding that cannot be taught but must be experienced firsthand. Having led teams throughout his entire career, he has developed a vast array of skills in business development, marketing, sales, capital raising, and technology.Charlie developed a personal interest in equities from a young age. This evolved to successfully raising', 'Greater Melbourne Area', 'Senior operator with extensive ANZ market experience.', ARRAY['Scaled Founder', 'Market Research / Strategy'], 'https://linkedin.com/in/charliecrozier', NULL, NULL, 'CCG', FALSE, '[{"name": "CCG"}, {"name": "VOLI"}]'::jsonb, NULL, ARRAY['australia'], NULL, 'charlie-crozier', 'Scaled Founder', ARRAY['international_entrant'], TRUE, FALSE)
